  "description": [
    "Cuba Is An Armed Communist Camp Senator Russell Says KhrushchevCastro Team Have Made The Brothers Kennedy Look Like Idiots As time moves on it becomes more evident that Khrushchev and Castro have made the administration in Wash ington look foolish When the administration found that Khrushchev was moving intercontinen tal missiles into Cuba the President took to the radio and TV in a speech electri fying the free world and the free world rallied to his support This gave him an excellent opportunity to get the Russian armed forces out of Cuba and to elimin ate Castro for good Yet instead of stand ing firm he faltered and in the opinion of a great many observers he made a trade with Khrushchev to move our mis sile sites out of Turkey and to perpetu ate Russian control on the island of Cuba His excuse was that Khrushchev had promised to remove his forces from Cuba Russians Building Up Today we find that the Russians are building up their armed forces in Cuba instead of withdrawing and Senator Richard B Russell of Georgia Chair man of the Armed Forces Committee of the Senate recently pictured Cuba as an armed Communist state"
  ],
